sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as Trace Harness / Caller
    participant DI as Shared DI Composition
    participant Descriptor as BridgeToolDescriptor
    participant Manifest as BridgeToolManifest
    participant Catalog as CompiledBridgeToolCatalog
    participant Executor as BridgeToolExecutor
    participant SecurityContext as ToolExecutionSecurityContext
    participant Policy as IToolExecutionPolicy
    participant Approval as IToolExecutionApprovalService
    participant Tool as RegexTextSearchTool
    participant Audit as IAuditSink
    participant Log as RecordingBridgeLogger

    Caller->>DI: AddBridgeToolServices()
    DI-->>Caller: IBridgeToolCatalog + IBridgeToolExecutor
    Caller->>Catalog: GetTools()
    Catalog->>Descriptor: RegexTextSearchTool.Descriptor
    Descriptor->>Manifest: derive manifest
    Manifest-->>Caller: id/name/version/category/source/discovery/host/risk/capabilities/approval
    Caller->>Executor: ExecuteAsync(tool-manifest-trace-20260516-req-001)
    Executor->>Log: Information execution started
    Executor->>Log: Trace redacted request payload
    Executor->>Catalog: TryGetTool("bridge.regexTextSearch")
    Catalog-->>Executor: RegexTextSearchTool
    Executor->>Descriptor: read descriptor manifest
    Descriptor->>Manifest: derive manifest
    Executor->>Log: Trace manifest metadata
    Executor->>SecurityContext: new(request, descriptor)
    SecurityContext->>Manifest: expose derived manifest
    Executor->>Policy: EvaluateAsync(SecurityContext)
    Policy-->>Executor: Allow, observed manifest id/version/category/source/host
    Executor->>Approval: skipped because ApprovalRequirement=NotRequired
    Executor->>Tool: ExecuteAsync(regex request)
    Tool-->>Executor: Success, 2 matches
    Executor->>Log: Information execution completed
    Executor->>Audit: RecordAsync(BridgeAuditEnvelope)
    Audit-->>Executor: manifest metadata in envelope metadata
    Executor-->>Caller: BridgeToolResult with request/operation correlation

    Note over Approval: Harness-only approval probe separately observed ToolExecutionApprovalContext.Manifest for an approval-required descriptor without adding a production tool.
    Note over Catalog: MEF path is described from existing MefFakeBridgeTool test evidence only; no MEF production behavior changed.
